lyrics:
[Verse]
Noah, he works in an office nine to five
Always typing away, keeping the dream alive
In a world of papers, he finds his daily grind
But his spirit soars as he leaves it all behind

[Chorus]
Oh, Noah, won't you break free from this routine
Let your soul dance, be the one to intervene
Open up your heart, embrace the melody
Noah, find your rhythm and set your spirit free
